queries.sql: SELECT `appointment`.*, `doctorprofile`.*, `client`.`client` as `clientName`, `doctorprofile`.`FirstName` as `doctorFirstName`, `doctorprofile`.`LastName` as `doctorLastName`, `fee_type`.`FeeType` as `appointmentTypeName` FROM `appointment` JOIN `doctorprofile` ON `doctorprofile`.`DoctorID` = `appointment`.`doctorID` JOIN `client` ON `client`.`idClient` = `appointment`.`clientID` JOIN `fee_type` ON `fee_type`.`f_id` = `appointment`.`appointmentType` WHERE ( `client`.`client` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR `doctorprofile`.`FirstName` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR `doctorprofile`.`LastName` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR `appointment`.`appointmentDate` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR `appointment`.`appointmentTime` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR `fee_type`.`FeeType` LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' OR (appointment.appointmentFee + appointment.hospitalCharges) LIKE '%te%' ESCAPE '!' )
